snippet.title: Nova Lands - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: A new gameplay trailer for Nova Lands has arrived and it showcases the game's visuals and content still in development. Nova Lands is a factory building, exploration, and island management game. Explore, engage in combat, and automate your industry. The planet you’re on is full of mysteries, creatures, people, and things to do. Welcome to your new home amongst the stars!
